{"tid":820063,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Warface 介紹/討論","createTime":"2018-09-15T08:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T08:47:21.000Z","uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a90e8062da1495a15816a59abc18a1db3dcc9d6e","tid":820063,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Warface</div></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/155426_cd7eeef4a2fc7c0e9025ec71a762d314.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F155426_cd7eeef4a2fc7c0e9025ec71a762d314.png&h=74531493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2013出 都算係老Game <br />\n不過隻Game係...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">免費</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n模式:<br />\nTeamdeath match<br />\n食雞 （32人）<br />\nCapture<br />\nPlant bomb/Defuse<br />\n仲有PVE<br />\n<br />\n有得自己set配件（鏡 消音 手桿位）<br />\n<br />\n免費Game 唯有靠賣點數槍賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點數槍性能比較好 屈傷害 唔飄<br />\n除咗點槍 仲有點甲 鞋 手套 可以屈爆你防<br />\n<br />\n靠Vendor解鎖槍都有啲勁槍 不過可能要玩一排先解鎖到（Vendor point每玩完一場都有得賺，可以用黎解鎖 槍 防具 配件 新手建議先解鎖<span style=\"color: red;\">配件</span> 勁嘅Vendor槍要好後期先有）<br />\n<br />\n間唔中有活動可以用遊戲錢買點槍 留意官網活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://由my.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%94%B1my.com&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=59f8a0f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">由my.com</a>營運（新營運商） 可經Steam登入<br />\nSteam: <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/291480/Warface/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F291480%2FWarface%2F&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=dd7615c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/291480/Warface/</a><br />\n<br />\n新開帳戶有野送 詳情參考以下Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=18185&amp;snA=281&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=0&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D18185%26snA%3D281%26bpage%3D1%26top%3D0%26ltype%3D&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fd5acc54\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=18185&amp;snA=281&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=0&amp;ltype=</a><br />\n<br />\n有唔明可以留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡覆"},{"pid":"a75c17460e50f78412ca0077ea745cb53369f56d","tid":820063,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fe24116a7cabd06f3fbb04dfa5df23f8854dc6","tid":820063,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}